# SEO & Localization Strategy

## Multi-Language Support
- **Languages**: Italian (it), English (en), German (de), Spanish (es)
- **Translation files**: [lang/](mdc:lang/) directory structure
- **Default locale**: Italian (user preference)

### Language Files Structure
```
lang/
├── it/app.php (primary)
├── en/app.php
├── de/app.php
└── es/app.php
```

## SEO Implementation

### Structured Data (Schema.org)
- **CreativeWork**: For solved puzzles
- **Game**: Sudoku puzzle classification  
- **WebApplication**: Main solver interface
- **BreadcrumbList**: Navigation structure
- **SearchAction**: Site search functionality

### Meta Tags & Open Graph
- Dynamic title/description generation
- Canonical URLs for permanent links
- Twitter Card support
- Language-specific meta content

### URL Structure
```
/{locale}/solve - Main solver page
/{locale}/solve/this-sudoku-puzzle/{hash} - Permanent links
/{locale}/solve/{difficulty}-sudoku-puzzle/{hash} - SEO URLs
```

