## Route Localization
File: [routes/web.php](mdc:routes/web.php)

### Pattern
```php
Route::prefix('{locale}')->group(function () {
    Route::get('/solve', function($locale) {
        return app(PublicSolverController::class)->index();
    })->name('localized.public-solver.index');
});
```

## Translation Best Practices
- Use `@switch(app()->getLocale())` in views
- Extract complex translations to PHP variables
- Avoid Blade directives within JSON-LD
- Maintain consistency across all languages

## Performance Considerations
- Cache translated content
- Lazy load non-critical language assets
- Optimize images with language-specific alt text
- Use CDN for static multilingual assets